Welcome.....

Yet again, another average day.... But life is good nonetheless. No?

I saw my cousin's play today, and then went back to her house for a party-ish-like-thing. Me, my brother, and my cousin, Jezzica soon became bored, so went outside only to be taunted by some hillbillies who live across the street. Stupid hoes....

But anywho, thats pretty much it for today.                          

                                       Ta,                                                       

                                              Sydney

*sigh* Man my life is gettin' boring... Right now, just looking up some info on bands and drawing at the same time.  And yes, yes I know what your thinking.  I am very talented.

Bye for now, Sydney

Hello Peo-*looks at last entry*....Wow...I'm boring.

But anywho, nothing new today.  An underaged kid hit on me, but other than that...

                                           Later-

                                                 Sydney

Hi y'all! Today was a pretty good day over all. Spent the day walking around the block with my cousin, and although how boring that may sound its pretty fun, plus you get excercise. We saw my cousin's crush named Travis(some scary dude who claims he smokes pot) and this other kid named Spencer who has a crush on me, ugh. He's some ugly 13-year-old who's role model is Eminem...NOT my type of guy. So after all that walking we headed to my house where the fact that my dad is a complete stereotypical JACKASS became more evident. He thinks that my cousin is a "punk" and because of this he thinks I'm gonna go around smoking pot and whatnot! I get strait A's and he still can't trust me enough...But anywho, after some talking with my cousin(by the way her name is Jezzica) I listened to some Dashboard Confessional and then everything was all better, lol.

                  See y'all around,
                       Sydney
